Well I think the - the majority of - of youngsters - knew that the policeman was a man who - who we had to watch, and - and - and not do anything that we should not do. And - and if - and if we did we would probably get - slapped by him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3539663 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12722762\charrsid5445546 Do you think that the policemen were usually quite fair?
