\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1124936\charrsid5445546 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12722762\charrsid5445546 ren't brutal in any way I mean they were - I think they were quite fair.
