Yes, well I can't - I - I don't know that it made any immediate - material difference. Probably my mother had some money - saved that she - she had saved.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3539663 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12722762\charrsid5445546 You told me he was out of work just a couple of times?
