\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3539663 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12722762\charrsid5445546 
When there was somebody in the district whom people disapproved of very strongly was there any special way in which they showed it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9257285 GE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12722762\charrsid5445546 
No, I don't think so. We might - as - as children we might be told that we mustn't play with Tommy so and so or - that's about the only thing that I can - any - any - disapproved of, the - it might have been -
 for other causes other than - that we shouldn't play with them, there might be an infection in the house or mups or something like that or - but - I - I - that's probably the only thing it was.
