e then you see, when - for instance, the day war was declared in 1914 I was transferred from Jarrow to - to Glasgow. And I - then from {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Glasgow{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 I was transferred to Rosseith until I - I was allowed to go into the forces in - 1916.
