 I got further promotion and went to Horden as a manager of the Horden Exchange. That's in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Durham{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, yes.
